    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014absolutely spotless inside and out, and it still has that fresh car smell! I\u2019ve babied this ride since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s been kept in truly perfect shape, this is the one for you. Drop me a message and come take it for a spin\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
