    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade vehicle that has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment since new. The exterior boasts a deep, showroom-quality luster with absolutely no swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections to the original paint. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the premium leather upholstery shows zero signs of bolster wear, and even the original factory scent is remarkably preserved. Every electronic component, switch, and mechanical system operates with precision. This car comes with a complete, transparent history including a comprehensive folder of service records from authorized dealerships. From the spotless engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, this vehicle is virtually indistinguishable from the day it left the showroom floor. A rare find for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
